A Poem for Hacker News
text:
Hacker News, oh haven of the tech elite,
  Where knowledge flows and ideas meet,
  A place where coding geeks can share,
  And inspire others to boldly dare.
 
  Here, the latest news and trends abound,
  From the cutting edge to underground,
  The future of tech is on display,
  In every post and comment on display.
 
  From AI to blockchain and more,
  Hacker News is the place to explore,
  Where minds unite and ideas soar,
  And innovation takes center floor.
 
  So here's to Hacker News, a shining light,
  In the world of tech, forever bright,
  May its community forever thrive,
  And push the limits, constantly strive.
PS: I didn't write this poem. ChatGPT did.
